data.revised_prompt: Envision an adorable baby sea otter. Imagine it basking in the shimmering sunlight as it merrily floats along the sapphire blue waters. The otter's soft, brown fur gleaming brilliantly and a hint of playful mischief in its dark, round eyes. A slender tail sways gently with the ebb and flow of the waters, as its tiny paws occasionally splash playfully. The ambiance is calm, serene, the gentle lap of waves visible nearby, with the endless expanse of sky meeting the sea at the horizon.
